<!-- MESSAGE FROM THE HOD -->
<section class="hod-message">
  <h2 class="hod-title">Message from the Head of Department</h2>
  <p class="hod-text">
    Dear Students and Esteemed Colleagues,<br><br>
    My Hearty Wishes to you all !!<br><br>
    It gives me immense pleasure to unveil this edition of our department newsletter. Each page in it 
    reflects the energy, creativity, and achievements of our vibrant student and faculty community. Over 
    the past months, our department has witnessed remarkable academic accomplishments, inspiring 
    events, and initiatives that showcase the true spirit of learning and leadership<br><br>

    This newsletter is a celebration of our shared journey. In the past quarterly, our faculty excelled 
    in Journal publications and Patent publications. Our department is consistently maintaining good 
    placements with our students getting recruitment in esteemed companies like <b>Morgan Stanley, BNY 
    Mellon, SAP Labs, MUFG Global Services and Oracle</b>.<br><br>

    I extend my heartfelt appreciation to all contributors, faculty members, and students whose 
    enthusiasm has helped in highlighting the reputation of the department. Their dedication reminds us 
    that growth happens when we work together and support one another.<br><br>

    As you read through this edition, I hope you feel the same pride and motivation that guided us in 
    creating it. May this newsletter inspire you to explore new ideas, participate actively, and continue 
    making meaningful contributions to our college community.<br><br>

  </p>

  <div class="hod-signature">
    <p><b>Dr. M. Lakshmi</b></p>
    <p>Professor & Head,<br>Department of Networking and Communications,<br>
    SRM Institute of Science and Technology</p>
  </div>
</section>

