    <li>M.Tech. Cloud Computing</li>
    <li>M.Tech. Cyber Security</li>
    <li>M.Tech. Forensics</li>
    <li>M.Tech. Internet of Things</li>
    <li>Ph.D. in Computer Science & Engineering</li>
  </ul>
  <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4"> Collaboration with Great Learning </h5>
